Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.16,0:01:19.56,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}今日が過去に替わることで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.76,0:01:23.15,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}明日が近づいて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.40,0:01:26.88,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}そんな当たり前のことに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.14,0:01:30.40,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}心は傷ついた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.13,0:01:32.65,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}あの日見た世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.97,0:01:34.48,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}もう一度作ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.82,0:01:38.04,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}かなう時がいつか来るなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.47,0:01:39.97,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}もう何もいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:41.78,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}まるで可能性が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.42,0:01:47.76,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}ないと誰に揶揄されても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:52.65,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}次の君に会える日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:56.57,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}繰り返しめぐる運命が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.83,0:01:59.90,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}たとえどんな道でも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:03.56,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}決して決してあきらめない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:05.40,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}明日またね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:07.33,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}その未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.51,0:02:11.12,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}いつまでもなくさないように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:14.60,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}終わりのない始まり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:16.64,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}今君と
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.06,0:02:20.05,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}夢見たいから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.31,0:02:22.07,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}つないだ手を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:27.84,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}離さないでね
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------OPCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.16,0:01:19.56,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}用现在覆盖过去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.76,0:01:23.15,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}未来就是这样步步走近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.40,0:01:26.88,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}如此理所当然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.14,0:01:30.40,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}却依旧心殇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.13,0:01:32.65,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}那天你我所见的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.97,0:01:34.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}再一次拼凑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.82,0:01:38.04,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}愿望实现之时若能到来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.47,0:01:39.97,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}我再无所求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:47.76,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}即使被人嘲笑不切实际
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:52.65,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}直到再见你为止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:59.90,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}纵使颠沛轮回的命运再艰辛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:03.56,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}我也绝对  绝对  不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:05.40,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}明天再见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:07.33,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}那一份未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.51,0:02:11.12,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}让我们一直珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:14.60,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}一旦开始  再无休止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:16.64,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}现在我只愿和你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.06,0:02:20.05,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}去瞭望梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.31,0:02:22.07,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}紧握的双手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:27.84,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}不会再分离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:10.97,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夕暮れ　帰り道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.69,0:22:16.03,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}並んで歩く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.82,0:22:21.12,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}オレンジ色の空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.88,0:22:26.50,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}街を包んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:28.45,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.62,0:22:36.51,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気を出して打ち明けた気持ちに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.26,0:22:45.24,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君はどんな答えをくれるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:48.06,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}変えられない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.39,0:22:51.55,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}また変えてしまいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.91,0:22:56.65,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}失われた時を探して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.01,0:23:01.80,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君といたあの季節
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.13,0:23:05.48,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日また会えるよね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:09.50,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君と会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.04,0:23:12.34,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}未来に届け
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.98,0:23:18.66,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか出会うまで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:10.97,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夕阳西下的归途
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.69,0:22:16.03,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一路同行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.82,0:22:21.12,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}橘黄色的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.88,0:22:26.50,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}包裹了小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:28.45,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我的深爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.62,0:22:36.51,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}拿出勇气向你表白的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.26,0:22:45.24,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你又会有怎样的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:48.06,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无法改变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.39,0:22:51.55,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}却又想要改变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.91,0:22:56.65,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}寻找遗失的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.01,0:23:01.80,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}和你同在的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.13,0:23:05.48,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天再会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:09.50,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}愿与你相会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.04,0:23:12.34,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}传向未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.98,0:23:18.66,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}直到相会那天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳  佳织
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.43,0:00:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏  你  你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.26,0:00:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.27,0:00:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的不是的  什么都没做  我什么都没做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个人倒在这儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.23,0:00:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  不过还是有呼吸的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.69,0:00:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  是不是叫辆救护车比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.15,0:00:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  还是说应该先叫老师来呢  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识她？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.25,0:00:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不认识啦  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.22,0:00:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  你认识我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.87,0:00:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  你的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字是  结
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.41,0:00:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是  古川结
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.02,0:01:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.35,0:01:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古川同学
