Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.74,0:23:29.77,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,350)\fad(200,200)}死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.33,0:23:30.43,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,350)\fad(200,200)}会长好像很开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.10,0:23:31.60,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,350)\fad(200,200)}都是因为我进行了干涉
